// Core library: the binary protocol.
//
// Low-level serialization and closure-introspection operations —
// `serialize_value`, `deserialize_value`, `closure_hash`,
// `closure_captures`, `handler_methods`, `hex_to_binary`,
// `binary_to_hex` — as intrinsics that compile to dedicated opcodes. They
// attach to this module at registration (`intrinsics_for_module`), so it
// carries no source declarations of its own.
